# AIStudio — operator scripts (gitignored, travels via BUNDLE)
# All operator tooling uses the _ops suffix → ignore by pattern (current + future).
*_ops.sh
*_ops.py
*_ops
# Any _ops file regardless of extension (.yaml/.txt/...) — §23 intent: operator-only, never tracked.
# Closes the ingest_test_ops.yaml leak the .sh/.py/bare rules missed (KRR_064).
*_ops.*
